data.description: This Beautiful home sits at the end of a cul-de-sac on a large lot with only one next door neighbor and a walking trail to the left. This home features a relaxing backyard with outdoor kitchen right next to the pool with a cozy firepit!  The open floor plan makes this home warm and inviting and so versatile with a great bedroom downstairs and a centrally located office. The luxury continues upstairs with the Primary bedroom, along with 3 more bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms! The loft upstairs offers extra space for hanging out and studying.
